item.description:
What is it all about? From the pandas docs: &ldquo;pandas is an open source, BSD-licensed library providing high-performance, easy-to-use data structures and data analysis tools for the Python programming language.&quot;
From the Koalas docs: &ldquo;The Koalas project makes data scientists more productive when interacting with big data, by implementing the pandas DataFrame API on top of Apache Spark.&quot;
First thing first,
Setting up the environment You can use any Apache Spark environment that suits you.
